name: Ge GE 76572 Dual Jack Cord, 25ft JAS76572

reviews.name: GE 76572 Dual Jack Cord, 25'
reviews.reviewText: Overall this product is heavy duty and well made. Very easy to install and it really helped me out with my communication needs.
reviews.title: Great Value

reviews.name: GE 76572 Dual Jack Cord, 25'
reviews.reviewText: We only have one phone jack in our living room, dinning room and kitchen and with this 25 ft jack cord, I can put a phone almost anywhere I need to and with the dual jack plug, I can also have 2 phones, however, to get the full use from the second phone, you will need another long cord so the phones aren't close to one another. Great buy at just 5 bucks too!
reviews.title: Great Product

reviews.name: GE 76572 Dual Jack Cord, 25'
reviews.reviewText: excellent, excellent, excellent and I love it.
